{"word":"G1836 - ἑξῆς - hexēs - hex-ace' - After","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἑξῆς</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hexēs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hex-ace'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">After</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"மறு, பின்பு - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"successively, in order"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2192 - ἔχω - échō - ekh'-o/2192\">G2192</a> (in the sense of <i>taking hold</i> of, that is, <i>adjoining</i>); <i>successive:</i> - after, following, X morrow, next.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}